{"tid":1298623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"必須支持狙擊TVB商場活動 同時喺度收集反TVB嘅口號","createTime":"2019-07-09T02:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T13:22:01.000Z","uid":69568,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"08916ee7a989477c976bb95d5ae23008b8f294fa","tid":1298623,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"TVB係商業機構 要反佢就必須要痛擊佢收入來源 (唔好講乜撚紅色資本 唔記得亞視點死？)<br />\n杯葛廣告都係另一種手法<br />\n廣告同新聞部都冇直接關係 唔通又唔搞？<br />\n仲有要反嘅又點止新聞部<br />\n佢成日買支那劇出賣本土文化 勁歌金曲又圍威喂 又大台霸權<br />\n咁多年嚟對TVB嘅不滿 已經忍無可忍<br />\n一路靠嗰800個盒打飛機 就Keep到所謂高收視<br />\n依家搵到個咁好嘅反抗方法 仲唔食住上？<br />\n<br />\n反TVB商場Show 令佢杯弓蛇影 係咁取消<br />\n如果佢照搞 就舉牌+嗌反TVB口號<br />\n等佢全場冇引 我哋又和理非 佢冇權叫實Q趕人<br />\n況且人數夠多 佢咩都做唔到啦 <br />\n長遠成功嘅 D商場以後仲敢唔敢搵佢商演？<br />\n<br />\n所以狙擊TVB商演係勢在必行嘅<br />\n喺度想收集大家嘅反TVB口號<br />\n到時就可以一齊嗌 要夠抵死夠啜核又順口嘅<br />\n<br />\n暫時多數口號都係針對新聞部<br />\n例如：無線新聞 出賣港人<br />\n<br />\n如果有咩口號係用無線電視/TVB/CCTVB開頭<br />\n應該集思廣益 大家一齊嗌爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好再潔癖<br />\nTVB上至金主 董事局 管理層<br />\n下至藝人 記者 後製 冇一個係好人<br />\n今次係反TVB最有機會成功嘅一次 <br />\n一定要一鼓作氣"},{"pid":"5f41664fadaed55135dc447d12ae032133d017fa","tid":1298623,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:21:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a4d67dece691094ed46e30c7599a56d9756e735e","tid":1298623,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n反完林鄭就可以專心反tvb"},{"pid":"2f384301b1b427e4b9b9685cb8036a2ff0cee222","tid":1298623,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"無線電視 厚顏無恥<br />\n無線新聞 出賣港人"},{"pid":"9006b37fae4532d07169e3059f35924d15bace93","tid":1298623,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f384301b1b427e4b9b9685cb8036a2ff0cee222","tid":1298623,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"無線電視 厚顏無恥<br />\n無線新聞 出賣港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:25:01.000Z","msg":"借：無線新聞 愚弄市民"},{"pid":"dc1ac0436dcd246f059038cdf7005421a5cf256e","tid":1298623,"uid":254165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:25:45.000Z","msg":"7月13有宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d904f125795c2987090f69ea167f075d8586c7c6","tid":1298623,"uid":269453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2368763829846386/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F2368763829846386%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=41afe3f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/2368763829846386/?ref=share</a>"},{"pid":"a00ebe2b7ea20bd0f5db3df78e5190bbd32c6687","tid":1298623,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:02:51.000Z","msg":"同tvb商場show打打氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c386c1bae1880fe77dba776753653d1fe75d3b","tid":1298623,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"無線新聞 出賣港人"},{"pid":"6982304b53e4449a1cf9d63cf256bd078b4a390b","tid":1298623,"uid":206522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:42:49.000Z","msg":"無限新聞 偏頗過人"},{"pid":"f6fd84f6d0df7828d4b724fcccf702ee40cef74a","tid":1298623,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T10:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd37f28065a8b0a62bb53ed75470e15eb5b34915","tid":1298623,"uid":206522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-0